platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 自分だけのJurassic World™ をつくりましょう!

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Evolve your dinos in lush landscapes

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This breathtaking game mixes tycoon-style park management with electrifying dino-on-dino battles, starring characters and critters from the blockbuster movie. We love tinkering with our dinosaur DNA to evolve our thunder lizards into more powerful specimens while also expanding our dream park’s high-tech facilities. When it comes time to test your dinosaurs’ mettle in the arena, strength and strategy are the keys to prehistoric pugilist victories. And luckily, the Indominus rex stays inside her cage. For now.
